{"tid":1874321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國將要求香港入境旅客必須提供有效的手機號碼及地址才可入境","createTime":"2020-02-11T06:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T05:15:51.000Z","uid":164771,"like":290,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"215d43303c3b4f624cf815bf01e38b38fa438429","tid":1874321,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"韓國將香港及澳門劃為疫區，明日12日凌晨零時起，所有從香港，澳門及中國入境韓國的乘客，每人必須提供有效的手機號碼及地址。<strong>韓國當局將會於入境櫃檯即場檢查，無法提供或提供虛假資料會被拒絕入境。酒店或民宿電話號碼不能當作聯絡號碼。遊客須開啟漫遊服務，以作追查。</strong>只有上網功能的電話卡不會被接納。<br />\n<br />\n不論人數，每人需提供各自手機號碼。另外，每位進入韓國的外國人，需下載自我診斷手機應用程式以記錄每日身體狀況。如果未能於登機櫃檯提供地址及電話，將不獲辦理登機手續。手機程式iOS版本會稍後推出。"},{"pid":"4e8f6a717826843d5a5c9f9d0b24114e9f624f8d","tid":1874321,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喺屋企家居隔離緊？<br />\n無口罩出唔到街？<br />\n咁快啲過嚟<span style=\"color: blue;\">Twitter</span>戰線！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要光復香港撳幾個掣都唔得？</span></span><br />\nTwitterHelpBot嘅tasklist 24小時更新<br />\n入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b68be815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">RT + Like + Comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. Rick Scott <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1226912446767562759?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1226912446767562759%3Fs%3D09&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=d8519b13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1226912446767562759%3Fs%3D09&h=820e2363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1226912446767562759?s=09</a><br />\n2. Josh Hawley <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1226896478968348679?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1226896478968348679%3Fs%3D09&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=7e147533\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1226896478968348679%3Fs%3D09&h=868754c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1226896478968348679?s=09</a><br />\n3. John Cornyn <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JohnCornyn/status/1226947238917746694?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJohnCornyn%2Fstatus%2F1226947238917746694%3Fs%3D09&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=55e650df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJohnCornyn%2Fstatus%2F1226947238917746694%3Fs%3D09&h=cc486fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JohnCornyn/status/1226947238917746694?s=09</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter核爆料要人】美國參眾議員狂插中國軍方偷取美國國民資料<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874234</a>"},{"pid":"962a81ce7add028a10da131c121cddb27de20b61","tid":1874321,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267eabbe0325c49413be742e5b57a48f1275efa7","tid":1874321,"uid":25468,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"要專登買張當地號碼嘅電話卡 , 一落機就要 active 張卡啟用"},{"pid":"6ef80065f9cb976937e197193a5437c0b32893ad","tid":1874321,"uid":100443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"有冇source?"},{"pid":"189260a44dbaacf142